{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be innovative and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artful Creations - Local Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #2a609c;\n            --secondary-blue: #4a86b9;\n            --text-color: #f8f9fa;\n            --background-color: #0d1b2a;\n            --accent-color: #1b263b;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-blue);\n            min-height: 70px;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            border-bottom: #e0e0e0 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0 10px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        #showcase {\n            min-height: 500px;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--secondary-blue) 0%, var(--brand-blue) 70%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        #showcase h2 {\n            font-size: 50px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        #showcase p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item-info p {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal Styles */\n        .modal {\n            display: none;\n            position: fixed;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            left: 0;\n            top: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            overflow: auto;\n            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);\n            padding-top: 60px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .modal-content {\n            margin: 5% auto;\n            display: block;\n            max-width: 80%;\n            max-height: 80%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .close-button {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 15px;\n            right: 35px;\n            color: #f1f1f1;\n            font-size: 40px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: 0.3s;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            z-index: 1001;\n        }\n\n        .close-button:hover,\n        .close-button:focus {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .modal img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .modal-caption {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ccc;\n            padding: 15px 15px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Artful Creations</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#showcase\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"showcase\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Discover Unique Art</h2>\n            <p>Explore a curated collection of paintings, sculptures, and digital art by a passionate local artist.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Gallery Highlights</h2>\n        <div class=\"gallery\">\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/2a609c/ffffff?text=Abstract+Blue\" alt=\"Abstract Painting\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/2a609c/ffffff?text=Abstract+Blue', 'Azure Dream', 'An exploration of color and form in various shades of blue.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Azure Dream</h3>\n                    <p>Abstract Oil on Canvas</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/4a86b9/ffffff?text=Sculpture+Detail\" alt=\"Sculpture Detail\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/4a86b9/ffffff?text=Sculpture+Detail', 'Oceanic Form', 'A mesmerizing sculpture inspired by the fluidity of water.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Oceanic Form</h3>\n                    <p>Bronze Sculpture</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/1b263b/ffffff?text=Digital+Art+Wave\" alt=\"Digital Art Wave\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/1b263b/ffffff?text=Digital+Art+Wave', 'Digital Tide', 'A vibrant digital artwork capturing the energy of a crashing wave.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Digital Tide</h3>\n                    <p>Digital Illustration</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/2a609c/ffffff?text=Landscape+Impression\" alt=\"Landscape Impression\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/2a609c/ffffff?text=Landscape+Impression', 'Coastal Serenity', 'An impressionistic landscape evoking a peaceful coastline.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Coastal Serenity</h3>\n                    <p>Acrylic Painting</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/4a86b9/ffffff?text=Portrait+Study\" alt=\"Portrait Study\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/4a86b9/ffffff?text=Portrait+Study', 'Blue Gaze', 'A captivating portrait study focusing on expressive eyes.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Blue Gaze</h3>\n                    <p>Charcoal Sketch</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/1b263b/ffffff?text=Abstract+Geometry\" alt=\"Abstract Geometry\" onclick=\"openModal('https://via.placeholder.com/800x600/1b263b/ffffff?text=Abstract+Geometry', 'Geometric Flow', 'A modern abstract piece exploring geometric patterns.')\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item-info\">\n                    <h3>Geometric Flow</h3>\n                    <p>Mixed Media</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n        <p>Driven by a lifelong passion for visual storytelling, the artist combines traditional techniques with contemporary flair. Their work often explores themes of nature, emotion, and the subtle beauty found in everyday life, with a particular fascination for the depth and tranquility of blue hues.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Interested in a commission or purchasing a piece? Feel free to reach out!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@artfulcreations.local\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-blue); text-decoration: none;\">info@artfulcreations.local</a></p>\n        <p>Follow on social media: <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-blue); text-decoration: none;\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-blue); text-decoration: none;\">Facebook</a></p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Artful Creations. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <div id=\"imageModal\" class=\"modal\">\n        <span class=\"close-button\" onclick=\"closeModal()\">&times;</span>\n        <img class=\"modal-content\" id=\"modalImage\">\n        <div id=\"caption\" class=\"modal-caption\">\n            <p class=\"modal-title\" id=\"modalTitle\"></p>\n            <p id=\"modalDescription\"></p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        function openModal(imgSrc, title, description) {\n            document.getElementById(\"modalImage\").src = imgSrc;\n            document.getElementById(\"modalTitle\").textContent = title;\n            document.getElementById(\"modalDescription\").textContent = description;\n            document.getElementById(\"imageModal\").style.display = \"block\";\n        }\n\n        function closeModal() {\n            document.getElementById(\"imageModal\").style.display = \"none\";\n        }\n\n        window.onclick = function(event) {\n            if (event.target == document.getElementById(\"imageModal\")) {\n                document.getElementById(\"imageModal\").style.display = \"none\";\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}